title: $%Splendidly Spacious in Silver Bluff! Adjacent to Douglas Park
posting_body: ['#$% Splendidly Spacious in Silver Bluff!', 'Adjacent to Douglas Park and just minutes from Coral Gables, Coconut Grove and Downtown Miami, this beautiful 3bed/2bath duplex unit is tucked away on a quiet dead-end street and boasts modern updates and bright open living.', "You'll love the large open kitchen with granite countertops with doors to the covered patio and private fenced-in backyard - so unique!", 'Entertaining is a breeze with the sun-drenched open living/dining room area, and the master suite is a dream with modern en-suite bath and roomy closets.', 'This rare-find unit also features bright 2nd and 3rd bedrooms with tons of storage and an in-unit utility room with side-by-side laundry machines.', 'PLUS, it comes with 3 parking spots!$%&', 'Self-employed, bad credit, no problem.', 'Text me, I respond immediately and have tons of inventory!', 'WE ARE ESSENTIAL BUSINESS FOR COVI19, WE ARE ALWAYS OPEN', 'CALL ME OR TEXT ME', 'Andy Zamudio', 'show contact info', 'We accept deposits with credit card if you are short of cash we help with that, we are the only company that accepts credit cards for deposits , zelle, cash app, paypal venmo payments accepted!!!', 'Aceptamos los depositos con tarjeta de credito sinud esta corto de cash, somos la unica compañia que lo acepta en Florida, zelle, cash app, paypal ,venmo.']
